title: America's 60 Greatest Unsolved Mysteries & Crimes (E2, S1)

sources.title: America's 60 Greatest Unsolved Mysteries & Crimes (E2, S1)
sources.description:
What is the Jersey Devil? The Mystery of the Little Big Horn. Who whacked Bugsy Siegel? Who fired the shot heard round the world? The Philadelphia Experiement. Who bombed Wall Street in 1920?
This compelling documentary series presents a countdown of America's 60 most notorious unsolved mysteries and crimes in a dramatic compilation revealing these unanswered questions in 10 fascinating episodes.
